g solutions, kitting, delivery, and pre-production services. In addition, it offers end-to-end logistics, surface and air express, air freight, and supply chain management and e-commerce solutions. Further, it offers export; import; ODC and hazardous cargo; ISO tank; warehouse bonded and general; and first and last mile solutions. The company was formerly known as Allcargo Global Logistics Limited and changed its name to Allcargo Logistics Limited in July 2011. Allcargo Logistics Limited was founded in 1989 and is based in Mumbai, India."}}